<item>
            <title>[LU-1192] Make Autotest support POSIX Compliance Testing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1192</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We manually run the LSB-VSX test suite from &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.opengroup.org/infosrv/lsb/ogdeliverables/LSB-VSX2.0-1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.opengroup.org/infosrv/lsb/ogdeliverables/LSB-VSX2.0-1/&lt;/a&gt; on Lustre filesystem to find the POSIX compliant issues.&lt;/p&gt;

